snippet: Alex Bilodeau, the Canadian who won gold at the 2010 Winter Games in Vancouver and again in Sochi in February, will become an accountant.
abstract: Alex Bilodeau, Olympic gold winner in moguls at 2010 Winter Games, announces he will retire and become an accountant.
lead_paragraph: Alex Bilodeau, the Canadian who won gold at the 2010 Winter Games in Vancouver and again in Sochi in February, will become an accountant.
